description: With this skill you can ask Alexa for a ski tip before hitting the slopes.  She can help get you ready for your lesson, and give you things to think about on your ski day.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask ski tip to tell me a ski tip
Alexa, ask ski tip, how about a ski tip
name: Ski Tip
shortDescription: Let Alexa help you ski better by asking her for a ski tip
